{"tid":1452080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[812]今日兩點又有民間記者會","createTime":"2019-08-11T23:46:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T04:57:56.000Z","uid":74888,"like":127,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"5ae0156f3cd0ba5bb2e9a5f5dcd8335c48f82d91","tid":1452080,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:46:22.000Z","msg":"各大傳媒機構、採訪主任、編輯及記者：<br />\n <br />\n民間記者會傳媒邀請函 <br />\n<br />\n第三次的民間記者會主題為：「『豬咀』背後，香港人保護香港人」。團隊希望能借是次機會，提供多角度意見，還原事實真相，從而回應警方及政府過去的謊言、以及社會的誤解和迷思。 <br />\n<br />\n現誠邀    貴機構派員出席採訪，詳情如下： <br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年8月12日<br />\n<br />\n時間：14：00<br />\n<br />\n記者會後將設有問答環節，由於會場座位有限，有興趣進場採訪的媒體請於 8月 11日（星期日）晚上11點30分或之前填妥附件資料，以電話（94377274）或電郵（pr640212@gmail.com ）覆示，以便安排。<br />\n <br />\n如有查詢，請聯絡金先生 （電話：94377274）。謝謝 <br />\n<br />\n此致<br />\n<br />\n採訪主任、編輯及記者 <br />\n<br />\n金先生    謹啟<br />\n<br />\n2019 年 8 月 11 日<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/citizenspresscon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcitizenspresscon&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkUXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=a4232ca2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/citizenspresscon</a><br />\n<br />\n不如順便集思廣益下睇下點樣可以令更多人知道/聽下呢個記者會講既野? <br />\n可能可以用黎拉中立派/淺藍過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n剪D重點出黎SHARE唔知得唔得?<br />\n<br />\n多謝黑警又比左我地一個難忘既晚上 <br />\n祝你地班黑警死全家 <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">唔知一次夠唔夠</span> <br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />撤惡法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />銷控罪<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />非暴動<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />查警暴<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真普選"},{"pid":"ed5121897eccdcd448f0fb1422b8aa01b3a53ea8","tid":1452080,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:49:08.000Z","msg":"早晨"},{"pid":"b98d0554b1c04cdd3ae5cf4fcad2be6c80b91c14","tid":1452080,"uid":42799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:50:19.000Z","msg":"早安"},{"pid":"13f1c92e0cc865b6414a31b1232663a0d72f2657","tid":1452080,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:51:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e1d5cca2c2106487413cbbdad5e877a9238c7789","tid":1452080,"uid":229489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:51:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb986646803c8448b26fcf55dce82a0127d360ca","tid":1452080,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:55:12.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"eaf5e73806c8b9ea3f807ed2321acfc03c5ba357","tid":1452080,"uid":74888,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:58:09.000Z","msg":"希望記者唔好再問關於佢地係唔係大台果D問題<br />\n將重點FOCUS返佢地講稿內容度<br />\n成日聽到佢地答&quot;我地唔係大台&quot;聽到厭"},{"pid":"c4097ac52fe4ed4fdf0bb42fe1496e3af2f449f0","tid":1452080,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eaf5e73806c8b9ea3f807ed2321acfc03c5ba357","tid":1452080,"uid":74888,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:58:09.000Z","msg":"希望記者唔好再問關於佢地係唔係大台果D問題<br />\n將重點FOCUS返佢地講稿內容度<br />\n成日聽到佢地答&quot;我地唔係大台&quot;聽到厭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:00:26.000Z","msg":"唔好問佢地之後會有咩行動之後會唔會升級<br />\n佢地唔係大台真係答唔到"},{"pid":"906f197210c83d77959b1a26b21656c6a39a450a","tid":1452080,"uid":74888,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c4097ac52fe4ed4fdf0bb42fe1496e3af2f449f0","tid":1452080,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eaf5e73806c8b9ea3f807ed2321acfc03c5ba357","tid":1452080,"uid":74888,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T23:58:09.000Z","msg":"希望記者唔好再問關於佢地係唔係大台果D問題<br />\n將重點FOCUS返佢地講稿內容度<br />\n成日聽到佢地答&quot;我地唔係大台&quot;聽到厭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:0